parameters:
\N<Riia>If only I were... If only I were a little stronger... like
my master... stronger...

\N<Riia>That's right, even Rame-chan would start to see me
differently... and maybe she'd rely on me a little...

\N<Riia>That's why... that's why I have to become stronger
quickly...!

\N<Zuuteruka>Good evening. You're working hard even at this late hour.
It's a bit warm, but it's a good night for training, isn't
it?
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehe... huhu... I see. So you're the kid from that time...
\N<Rame>Calling me to such a place... What do you want...?

\N<Red Cap Ulipo>But... you've been so cold lately. You hardly pay any
attention to me...
\N<Rame>Wait please... What do you mean by dating? I never...
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Hey, hey! Let's go somewhere now!? It'll definitely be fun!?

\N<Red Cap Ulipo>And then... you know... let's do it again after such a long
time...!
\N<Rozaro>Let go of her hand. Stop pestering her.

\N<Red Cap Ulipo>What's it to you, old man. It's none of your business, so
just shut up.

\N<Rozaro>Of course I don't know you, nor do I intend to get involved.
But can't you imagine what happens after a warning?

\N<Red Cap Ulipo>What's with that look... You're not going to use violence on
me, are you...!?
\N<Rozaro>It's not violence. If anything, it's education.
\N<Red Cap Ulipo>Do you understand!? Fubii is on my side! I'll tell on you!

\N<Rozaro>On the contrary, I'd like you to do just that. Tell him too,
not to involve himself with her ever again.

\N<Rozaro>I promised to protect you, didn't I? Can you trust me a
little now?

\N<Rame>Yes... I was very scared. Not so much because of him but
because of myself.

\N<Rame>I was wondering what's going to happen to me from now on.
Where did I go wrong.
\N<Rozaro>Don't worry. You haven't done anything wrong.

\N<Rozaro>If there is a mistake, it's theirs. Anything that hurts you
is wrong.

\N<Rozaro>Didn't I tell you before? Their mistakes are due to
immaturity. They don't know any better.

\N<Rozaro>That's why they hurt others without a second thought. They
hurt a delicate woman like you.
\N<Rame>Delicate... what do you mean by that...?

\N<Rozaro>It's because of your charm that makes me want to do this.
Your allure makes me want to act this way.

\N<Rozaro>But if you realize there's a mistake, you just have to take
it back. Most paths can be retraced, as long as the person
has the will to do so.
\N<Rame>Can I... can I really do it...?
\N<Rozaro>You can. I'll lend you the strength for it. So trust me.

\N<Rozaro>Don't doubt my existence, follow me. If you do, I'll remove
the obstacles that trouble you. Just like today... and
tomorrow, and the days after that.

\N<Rozaro>If you're as immature as they are, then rely on me. If
you're by my side, you won't stray from the path.
\N<Rozaro>Both Riia and you... let me guide you both.

\N<Rozaro>You are a precious friend to Riia. That makes you precious
to me as well.

\N<Rozaro>To protect that precious person, I will overcome any
obstacle.

\N<Rame>I... I want to become stronger... so that I won't disappoint
my master...
\N<Rozaro>Yes... leave it to me. I'll show you the way for that.
